data.description: Set against the breathtaking backdrop of Selah, Washington, this expansive ranch spans 7.87 acres of fertile land, offering an ideal canvas for cattle or horse enthusiasts. The main residence, a spacious three-bedroom, two-bathroom home, encompasses a generous 2311 square feet. Constructed in 1975, the house exudes a classic charm, perfectly complementing the natural beauty that surrounds it. The above-ground pool, though in need of renovation, holds promise for revitalization, presenting an exciting project for the discerning homeowner. From this elevated vantage point, the property affords sweeping vistas of the rugged foothills and the tranquil expanse of the Yakima River Canyon, creating an awe-inspiring backdrop to everyday life. Equipped with a fully insulated garage that adds both convenience and utility to this already impressive property. In addition to its splendid features, this Selah ranch includes a separate shop that further enhances its appeal. This versatile space provides ample room for storage, hobbies, or even potential workspace for projects and activities. With its generous acreage and commanding views, this Selah ranch promises a unique and idyllic living experience for those seeking a harmonious blend of rural charm and modern comfort. Call for a tour today! With a full price offer, the seller will be giving a $5,000 credit to the buyer at closing.
